 solution stephen burnett – chairman  ceo  koolbridge solar inc smart load center™ – printed circuit board  for initial testing  for prototype run design complete fabrication complete population underway smart load center™ – embedded software basic operating system in place task priorities task scheduling user interface under development led’s for load source lcd display for status communication port for configuration and testing electrical power interface under development monitor  breaker currents monitor  power currents  false false false false true false false auto true easeinout  false  true false previous left arrow key next right arrow key curr of total koolbridge solar smart load center™ testing in process a koolbridge solar embedded software engineer tests the smart load center™ for circuit by circuit switching capabilities what is smart solar contact us koolbridge solar in the news dr paul w dent produces his th video  press release koolbridge solar signs on  highly qualified and experienced north carolina solar installers  press release koolbridge solar named as one of five startups powering up the southeasts clean energy market  hypepotamuscom dr jaap haartsen the inventor of the bluetooth technology has joined koolbridge solar as a technology advisor  press release chris tridico moves into chief technology officer position at koolbridge solar  press release new ceo at koolbridge solar to drive revenue growth  wilmington biz koolbridge solar named  made winner in functional product category  greater wilmington business journal koolbridge solar named  of  finalists for energy and the environment by the nc technology association  north carolina technology awards koolbridge solar named finalist in nc tech awards  north carolina technology awards koolbridge solar signs  year agreement  with nc cleantech energy center at nc state koolbridge solar inc one of four new members  research triangle cleantech cluster find out how much solar energy can save you koolb