rt load center a solar and utility energy smart breaker box that can automatically select the use of utility power or solarderived power independently for each of a number of circuit breakers in a panel box and solar inverters the company was founded in  and is based in wrightsville beach north carolina b waynick boulevardwrightsville beach nc united statesfounded in  employees phone  koolbridgesolarcom key executives for koolbridge solar inc mr william f griffin chief executive officer and president age  mr john stephen burnett cofounder and chairman age  mr j phillips l johnston jd cofounder vice chairman chief legal officer corporate secretary and director age  dr paul w dent founder chief scientist and director age  mr lawrence d zirbel cofounder and director age  compensation as of fiscal year  koolbridge solar inc key developments koolbridge solar promotes william bill griffin as president and ceo feb   william bill griffin promoted to president and ceo at koolbridge solar bill brings to koolbridge solar an extensive amount of business development operations financial analysis business operations team building startup partner relationship building global distribution and government sales expertise as president and ceo he has been tasked by the koolbridge solar board of directors to build the company into the leading global provider of renewable energy solutions prior to joining koolbridge solar bill was an executive coach at cornerstone advisory partners koolbridge solar inc auditor raises going concern doubt oct   koolbridge solar inc filed its annual on oct   for the period ending dec   in this report its auditor daszkal bolton llp gave an unqualified opinion expressing doubt that the company can continue as a going concern similar private companies by industry company name region c technologies inc united states m technologies inc united states dc inc united states  electrical llc united states d energetics inc united states recent private companies transac